While the tiger and horse refused, the kind-hearted ox agreed to carry the rat across.

17
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:10,080
Yet, just as they were about to reach the other side, the rat jumped off the ox's head

18
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:13,080
